==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spheno-
<hw>Sphe"no-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A combining form used in anatomy to
indicate <xex>connection with</xex>, or <xex>relation to</xex>, <xex>the
sphenoid bone</xex>; as in <xex>spheno</xex>maxillary,
<xex>spheno</xex>palatine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sphenodon</ent>⟦br⟧
